                        How I learned about the bomb and learned to love it. 
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="nav">
                <ul class="sf-menu dropdown">
                    <li class="selected"><a href="#about_me">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#projects">Projects</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div id="body">
                <div id="content">
                    <div class="box">
                      <%= yield %>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="right_sidebar">
                    <div class="sidebar">
                        <ul>	
                            <li>
                            <h4><span>Quick Links</span></h4>
